&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;The stamp on the pig shows the acceptable quality of it&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;The girl keeps a diary every day&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;The man is submitting the report to his boss&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;I am just an ordinary man&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;Doing housework exhausts me&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;==The shirt is so cheap that l really want to purchase it==&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;I have an appointment with my doctor tomorrow&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;==What a waste to throw the food away==&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;The girl uses a pepper(胡椒粉) spray to protect herself&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;The man who holds the pan is her last enemy&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;The pupil(小学生;瞳孔) is completely immersed(沉浸的) in the glory of wearing a red scarf&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
