&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;Stop scratching the blackboard! The harsh noise is fring them crazy&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;She stays optimistic,despite her confition&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
